{"tid":1492180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位, 請把握接下來幾日輿論無敵時間","createTime":"2019-08-20T17:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T00:23:49.000Z","uid":51963,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f8d1affcd3b809b959b8ce7c9f70c41f2d7ba4a9","tid":1492180,"uid":51963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:07:17.000Z","msg":"尋日發生的幾件事, 為我地係輿論方面爭取到幾日無敵時間<br />\n呢幾日對家基本上係無得還手, 請鍵戰好好把握呢個機會做最多最有效文宜<br />\n<br />\n1. 開TWITTER用英文做文宣, 另外強調TWITTER封左20萬中國帳號單野, 短時間內要將中國帳號=只會發放假資訊呢點入外國TWITTER用戶腦, 對日後TWITTER輿論戰極關鍵<br />\n2. 請將斬人刀手形容為&quot;警察/極權政府支持者&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9nkaTHc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9nkaTHc.jpg&h=e7607849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&quot;Who is more violent and wins a fight, who is the boss&quot;<br />\n3. 斬人單野好多人都仲有包伏, 話&quot;禍不及妻兒/小朋友無辜&quot;, 對外文宣時請低調處理, 以輿論行先<br />\n(對內點都好, 一定不割蓆)<br />\n4. 警犬濫用私刑條片同運動無關, 但要話比世人知, 無CCTV既情況下, 示威者就會係咁既下場"},{"pid":"6bb69f0d48d3623d3a2cd1fe5fa5daefe1a34372","tid":1492180,"uid":51963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:10:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"935688a932f31aa2cc24b858c0670996010b9abc","tid":1492180,"uid":51963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:15:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"072fc3348b7e513cf36c61d7cbe3fd4800e607d0","tid":1492180,"uid":51963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:26:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"42d69862686510dece94d343d0198d6fd6dbd271","tid":1492180,"uid":51963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:36:12.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cb1f89c6f8a5062e0351917af13631a78d86246e","tid":1492180,"uid":125938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:37:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7abd15061a155dd87fbf83a167eca89ed91a42c","tid":1492180,"uid":51963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:40:01.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid"